01:48:49.480 --> 01:48:51.430
put a smile on your face

01:48:51.440 --> 01:48:54.030
and a song in your heart. Jesus loves

01:48:54.040 --> 01:48:55.990
you and we love you. God bless you all

01:48:56.000 --> 01:48:59.760
and we'll see you again. Bye-bye.

